  "url": "sec-democracy-voting.html#sec-democracy-voting-4-4",
  "type": "Example",
  "number": "6.2.1",
  "title": "",
  "body": "  Students are voting for their class president and the candidates are Omar (O), Ana (A), and Helena (H). They have ranked the candidates according to their preference.      Vien  Ana  Marv  Tasha  Eve  Omar  Lupe  Dave  Helena  Jimmy    1st choice  A  A  O  H  A  O  H  O  H  A    2nd choice  O  H  H  A  H  H  A  H  A  H    3rd choice  H  O  A  O  O  A  O  A  O  O      "
